 \psi: M \rightarrow Hom(\mathbb{N}^{+}, M) \\ m \mapsto \phi(n) 
 \phi(n) = \begin{cases} e_M, & \text{if }n\text{ is even} \\ m, & \text{if }n\text{ is odd} \end{cases} 
